                        Game..........: Deep Dungeons of Doom
                        Developer.....: Bossa Studios
                        Date..........: 23/12/2013
                        Version.......: 1.1.2
                        Language......: English
                        Genre.........: Rogue-Like Dungeon Crawler


---<<< Release info >>>-------------------------------------------------------

Deep Dungeons of Doom is a rogue-like game where you play as three adventurers trying to save the land from an ancient evil. Packing the best looking pixel art to ever appear in a game, Deep Dungeons of Doom is the 'Dark Souls' of mobile games as it grows very hard, very fast, and goes deep into easter eggs and hidden unlocks.

Not to worry, though, as the controls are epic for a touchscreen, and the game feels like the first dungeon/roguelike that was actually made for mobiles and tablets.

Play well, upgrade your skills at the shrines, venture forth and unlock the Deepest Dungeon of Doom for maximum adventuring fun.
